<i>noun</i>: 피폐 [피폐/피페], 피로 [피로], 피곤 [피곤], 쇠진 [쇠진/쉐진], 소진 [소진], 기진 [기진], 곤죽 [곤죽], 고갈 [고갈] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>피폐 [피폐/피페]</dt><br>
<dd>exhaustion; devastation</dd><br>
<dd>지치고 힘이 약해짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of becoming exhausted and weakened.</dd><br>
<dt>피로 [피로]</dt><br>
<dd>tiredness; exhaustion; fatigue</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 정신이 지쳐서 힘듦. 또는 그런 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>Being tired and worn-out physically or mentally, or such a state.</dd><br>
<dt>피곤 [피곤]</dt><br>
<dd>tiredness; exhaustion; fatigue</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 지쳐서 힘듦.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being tired and worn-out physically or mentally.</dd><br>
<dt>쇠진 [쇠진/쉐진]</dt><br>
<dd>exhaustion</dd><br>
<dd>힘이나 기운이 점점 약해져 없어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>Draining of strength or energy to a complete exhaustion.</dd><br>
<dt>소진 [소진]</dt><br>
<dd>exhaustion</dd><br>
<dd>점점 줄어들어 다 없어짐. 또는 다 써서 없앰.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making empty by decreasing gradually, or using something up completely.</dd><br>
<dt>기진 [기진]</dt><br>
<dd>exhaustion</dd><br>
<dd>힘을 모두 써서 지침.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of using up energy and becoming tired.</dd><br>
<dt>곤죽 [곤죽]</dt><br>
<dd>1. mushiness; muddiness</dd><br>
<dd>물이 많아 질퍽한 밥이나 땅.</dd><br>
<dd>Sticky steamed rice or muddy land because it contains large amount of water.</dd><br>
<dd>2. mess</dd><br>
<dd>일이 엉망이 된 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which things are messed up.</dd><br>
<dd>3. exhaustion; fatigue</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 술이나 병, 피로 등으로 힘없이 늘어진 몸.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) An extremely exhausted body due to heavy drinking, illness, fatigue, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>고갈 [고갈]</dt><br>
<dd>1. being dried up</dd><br>
<dd>물이 말라서 없어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>Water's running dry.</dd><br>
<dd>2. exhaustion; depletion</dd><br>
<dd>자원이나 물질 등이 다 써서 없어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a resource or material runs out.</dd><br>
<dd>3. being dried up; exhaustion</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 대상에 대한 느낌이나 생각이나 힘 등이 없어짐.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which a feeling or idea about something, or power, etc., is gone.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>